## Accordion

**Path**: `@/components/Accordion`  
**Figma**: Roy design system → accordion-basic (553:4285), accordion-ratings (553:1921).

Expandable panel(s). **AccordionItem**: trigger row (title + optional **headerRight** + chevron) + collapsible content. Padding 24px, 24px gap between trigger and content; trigger row 12px gap. **Title**: semi/body-lg (20px), slate-900 (hover slate-950, disabled grey-700). **headerRight**: optional node between title and chevron (e.g. ratings, badge, button); click does not toggle. Chevron: expand_more / expand_less in 40×40 area, transparent. **States**: default, hover, focus, disabled (bg grey-200). Content (when open): optional heading + body or any ReactNode.

**AccordionItem props**

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `title` | `string` | Yes | Trigger label |
| `headerRight` | `React.ReactNode` | No | Content in header between title and chevron (e.g. ratings, button) |
| `children` | `React.ReactNode` | Yes | Content when expanded |
| `open` | `boolean` | No | Controlled open |
| `onOpenChange` | `(open: boolean) => void` | No | When open changes |
| `defaultOpen` | `boolean` | No | Initial open (uncontrolled) |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | No | Disabled state |
| `className` | `string` | No | Root class |

**Accordion props** (wrapper with multiple items)

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `items` | `Array<{ title: string; headerRight?: React.ReactNode; content: React.ReactNode }>` | Yes | Items to render |
| `allowMultiple` | `boolean` | No | Allow multiple open (default false) |
| `value` | `number[]` | No | Controlled open indices |
| `onValueChange` | `(value: number[]) => void` | No | When open set changes |
| `className` | `string` | No | Root class |

**Exports**: `Accordion`, `AccordionItem`, `AccordionProps`, `AccordionItemProps`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { Accordion, AccordionItem } from "@/components/Accordion";

<AccordionItem title="Description" defaultOpen>
  <p className="font-medium text-grey-900 ...">Heading</p>
  <p className="text-grey-800 ...">Body text...</p>
</AccordionItem>

<AccordionItem title="Ratings" headerRight={<Badge variant="default">0 reviews</Badge>} defaultOpen>
  ...
</AccordionItem>

<Accordion
  items={[
    { title: "Description", content: <p>Content here.</p> },
    { title: "Ratings", headerRight: <span className="text-grey-500 text-sm">0 reviews</span>, content: <p>...</p> },
  ]}
  allowMultiple={false}
/>
```

