## Tabs

**Path**: `@/components/Tabs`  
**Figma**: Roy design system → Tabs (node 144:1012).

Horizontal tab list. Each tab: label + optional icon (24px), padding 8px 16px, gap 4px between label row and 2px underline. **Rest**: text grey-500, no underline. **Active**: text slate-900, 2px underline. **Hover**: text slate-950. **Disabled**: text grey-700, 2px slate-200 underline. Label: semi/body-md (16px).

**Props**

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `tabs` | `TabItem[]` | Yes | `{ id, label, icon?, disabled? }` per tab |
| `value` | `string` | Yes | Currently selected tab id |
| `onValueChange` | `(id: string) => void` | Yes | Called when a tab is selected |
| `className` | `string` | No | Applied to the root wrapper |

**Exports**: `Tabs`, `TabsProps`, `TabItem`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { Tabs } from "@/components/Tabs";

<Tabs
  tabs={[
    { id: "a", label: "Tab A" },
    { id: "b", label: "Tab B", icon: "account_circle" },
    { id: "c", label: "Tab C", disabled: true },
  ]}
  value={activeId}
  onValueChange={setActiveId}
/>
```

### TabsBox (box variant)

**Figma**: Tab-Variant-box (node 608:1926). Same folder: `@/components/Tabs`.

Vertical box per tab: icon (34×34) above label (medium/body-md 16px), optional warning Badge below. Right border (1px slate-200) between boxes; active: bg-slate-100. Width 95px per tab.

**Props**: `tabs: TabsBoxItem[]`, `value`, `onValueChange`, `className?`. **TabsBoxItem**: `id`, `label`, `icon` (required), `badge?: string`, `disabled?`.

**Exports**: `TabsBox`, `TabsBoxItem`, `TabsBoxProps`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { TabsBox } from "@/components/Tabs";

<TabsBox
  tabs={[
    { id: "orders", label: "Order", icon: "receipt_long", badge: "10" },
    { id: "ship", label: "Ship", icon: "local_shipping" },
  ]}
  value={activeId}
  onValueChange={setActiveId}
/>
```

