## Radio

**Path**: `@/components/Radio`  
**Figma**: Roy design system → radio button (24:2142), Radio list-items (26:2494).

Circle with optional inner dot when checked. **Sizes**: default 24×24 (inner dot 12px), large 32×32 (inner dot 16px). **States**: default (slate-100 bg, slate-900 border), hover (slate-200, slate-950), focus (ring), disabled (slate-200 border, grey-700 dot when checked), error (red-100 bg, red-600 border and dot). Optional **label** (26:2494): row, gap 4px (large) / 8px (default); typography medium/body-md (default size) or medium/body-lg (large size); label colors: default slate-900, hover slate-950, disabled grey-700, error red-700. Use same `name` and controlled `value` + `onChange` for groups.

**Props**

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
|------|------|----------|-------------|
| `value` | `string` | Yes | Value for this option (group by `name`) |
| `checked` | `boolean` | No | Whether this option is selected (controlled) |
| `name` | `string` | No | Input name – same for all options in group |
| `onChange` | `(e: React.ChangeEvent<HTMLInputElement>) => void` | No | Called when selection changes |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | No | Disabled state |
| `error` | `boolean` | No | Error state (red border/bg/dot) |
| `label` | `React.ReactNode` | No | Label next to radio (gap 4px large / 8px default, medium/body-md or body-lg per size) |
| `size` | `"default" \| "large"` | No | default 24×24, large 32×32 |
| `id` | `string` | No | Input id for form/label association |
| `aria-label` | `string` | No | Accessible name (when no `label`) |
| `className` | `string` | No | Root label class |

**Exports**: `Radio`, `RadioProps`.

**Example**

```tsx
import { Radio } from "@/components/Radio";

// Group: same name, parent holds selected value
const [selected, setSelected] = useState("a");
<Radio name="choice" value="a" checked={selected === "a"} onChange={() => setSelected("a")} label="Option A" />
<Radio name="choice" value="b" checked={selected === "b"} onChange={() => setSelected("b")} label="Option B" />

<Radio name="size" value="default" label="Default size" checked onChange={() => {}} />
<Radio name="size" value="large" size="large" label="Large" onChange={() => {}} />
<Radio value="x" disabled label="Disabled" />
<Radio value="x" checked error label="Error" onChange={() => {}} />
```

