## VariantDrawer

**Path**: `@/components/VariantDrawer` 
**Figma**: Roy design system → variant headers flow (node 410:10870), initial drawer (node 410:10422).

Drawer for creating and managing variant groups on a listing. **Single view** (no separate create vs edit screens): when no groups exist, a "Name your variant group" form with quick select is shown; once groups exist, the **active group** (first in the list) is shown at top with "Variant group: &lt;name&gt;", option list, add-option input, and "+ Add group" button. Other groups appear below as **collapsed accordions** (expand to view options). "+ Add group" is disabled until the active group has at least 2 options. Back and overlay click always close the drawer; if the active group is unfinished (fewer than 2 options), it is discarded on close. Uses `Drawer` + `DrawerTopBar` internally. Width 440px.

